data.description: Beautiful CBS 4/2/2 split floorplan home has been freshly painted with many upgrades! New design entry door, newly installed gutters/leaf system, plantation shutters, screened-in garage, extra-large lanai with new screen enclosure, completely fenced-in yard, solar panels ($105/month financing agreement to be transferred to new owners), new fans and light fixtures throughout the home, new sprinkler system, 2022 HVAC system, Water Heater, Washer/Dryer, Water Softener, Roomy backyard with enough room for a pool. Ceramic tile throughout common areas and deep-cleaned carpets in bedrooms - this one will not last! Minutes to Sams Club, Walmart, Home Depot, Lowes, Starbucks, many restaurants and the popular area of Tradition
